plmxml_bus:QueryClause.stringValue: SELECT qid FROM WorkspaceObject WHERE "object_name" = "${Name = }" AND "object_desc" = "${Description = }" AND "object_type" = "${Type = }" AND "owning_user.user_id" = "${OwningUser = $USERID}" AND "owning_group.name" = "${OwningGroup = $GROUP}" AND "creation_date" >= "${CreatedAfter = }" AND "creation_date" <= "${CreatedBefore = }" AND "last_mod_date" >= "${ModifiedAfter = }" AND "last_mod_date" <= "${ModifiedBefore = }" AND "date_released" >= "${ReleasedAfter = }" AND "date_released" <= "${ReleasedBefore = }" AND "release_status_list.name" = "${ReleaseStatus = }" AND "EPMTask:process_stage_list.object_name" = "${WorkflowTemplateName = }" AND "EPMTask:process_stage_list.fnd0StartedTasks.object_name" = "${CurrentTask = }" AND "active_seq" != "0"
